    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity, with a double VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced and a rear subframe that has undergone preventative reinforcement for maximum torsional rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate entry, transmitting power through a factory variable M differential lock. The exterior maintains its factory-original paint depth, while the cabin features Nappa leather sport seats with no discernible bolster compression or wear. Every individual throttle body is calibrated to factory specifications, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is reached with linear, aspirated precision. This is a turn-key, concours-level enthusiast vehicle with no deferred maintenance.",
